# Khmer OCR
## 1. API to generated OCR Text from base64 image : [ Method POST ]
```
http://khmerocr.open.org.kh/api/ocr_image_to_text
```
#### Sample of Post Json data to server 
```
[
	{
		"photo" : ""
	}
]
```
#### Result/Output
##### Successfully generated result
```
{
    "code": "200",
    "message": "success",
    "ocr_generated_text": " \n\n  10 \n 4 =   \n1   27\n\n \n  } .\n.  \n\n \n\n\n\n\n \n\f"
}
```
##### If result is blank
```
{
    "code": "404",
    "message": "Result is null",
    "ocr_generated_text": ""
}
```
##### If POST Data is not in JSON format
```
{
    "code": "500",
    "message": "Receiving data is not JSON format",
}
```
